946
00:58:27,440 --> 00:58:31,510
Then maybe Shimizu is stalling for time?

947
00:58:31,510 --> 00:58:33,320
I don't think that's the case.

948
00:58:33,320 --> 00:58:38,220
Shimizu probably has their own circumstances so they can't keep wasting time.

949
00:58:38,220 --> 00:58:42,430
So it's crucial to hide deadlines from each other.

950
00:58:42,430 --> 00:58:44,580
Deadline?

951
